            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are in the oven, peel and finely dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to caramelise</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-7-1657536171323-x200.jpg",
