            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the gratin is in the oven, dice your <strong>cucumber</strong></p><p>Bash your<strong> roasted peanuts </strong>roughly with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>diced cucumber</strong>, <strong>bashed peanuts</strong> and <strong>nigella seeds </strong>in a bowl with the juice from your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon[s] </strong>and a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>nutty cucumber salad</strong></p>",
