      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p><p>Serve the <strong>plant-based</strong> <strong>Indian spiced tomato & potato gratin </strong>with the<strong> nutty cucumber salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
